{"word":"ἀνακλάω","slug":"ἀνακλάω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἀνακλάω</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>Note also that there is another verb <a href='S:ἀνακλάω'><el>ἀνακλάω</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to bend back</i>, <el>δέρην</el> <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><i>to break short off</i>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}